item.description:
Come volunteer with us to support this festive 5K Road Race before famous St. Patrick's Day Parade in Southie. Est. 1940, race starts/ends at South Boston Boys & Girls Club.

Email Cathy at localservice@bostonrotaract.org to sign up or for more information.
